{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Planning complete after interactive refinement. Chosen MVP: compact closed creation_channel values cli/mcp/python/jira/import/unknown; explicit producer attribution for new CREATE events; deterministic three-signal Jira-only inference for legacy records with creation_channel_inferred=true; all other legacy records unknown. Actor, environment, source_*, mutation provenance, filtering, and security attestation remain out of scope. Decomposed into 6fe2 (local facades), e622 (Jira/import + inference), and 568c (SNAPSHOT durability), with sequential depends_on links because the reducer/docs surfaces overlap. File impacts and DD verification commands are recorded on the epic and every child."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784259240555601001,"uuid":"8a19b01e-b5ec-4194-af65-4509ac6c8936"}